<div id="banner">
<h1>Resolving my Deltas</h1>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="welcome">
    <%= image_tag "james_hi.png", size:"200x205", id: "james_hi", alt: "Edit Entry" %>
    <h2>Hi! Welcome to a collection of my ideas, blabberings, and shower thoughts. </h2>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. In convallis varius dui, a molestie turpis fermentum et. Duis id tristique sem, sed elementum felis. In at turpis tempor, eleifend felis non, venenatis tortor. Nam vel eleifend ligula. </p>
    <p>Nunc felis orci, pulvinar et nulla et, pharetra finibus lectus. Mauris a massa mattis, tristique neque non, pretium diam. Nullam felis felis, venenatis vel augue vitae, elementum bibendum lorem.</p>

  </div>
  <hr>

  <div class="row landing_bottom">
    <div class="col-md-9 landing_posts">
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <h2> <%= post.title %> </h2>
        <p><%= post.body %></p>
        <%= link_to 'See Post', post_path(post) %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 landing_aside">
      <%= form_tag(posts_path, :method => "get", class: "navbar-form", id: "search-form") do %>
         <div class="input-append">
           <%= text_field_tag :search, params[:search], class: "span2", placeholder: "Search Posts" %>
         </div>
      <% end %>
      <h2>Archive</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><a class="href">September</a></li>
        <li><a class="href">October</a></li>
        <li>November</li>
        <li>December</li>
        <li>January</li>
      </ol>
      <h2>Categories</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><a class="href">Rails</a></li>
        <li><a class="href">Node.js</a></li>
        <li>Tech</li>
        <li>Start-ups</li>
        <li>Policy</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path %>
</div>